### ================================ 自定义指标演示 ================================

### 演示 Counter 指标（每次请求 +1）
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator-demo/counter

### 演示 Timer 指标（模拟随机耗时 50~500ms）
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator-demo/timer

### 演示 Gauge 指标 — 添加队列元素
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator-demo/gauge/add

### 演示 Gauge 指标 — 移除队列元素
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator-demo/gauge/remove

### 演示 DistributionSummary 指标（记录请求负载大小分布）
POST http://localhost:8080/actuator-demo/distribution-summary
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "size": 1024
}

### ================================ Spring Actuator 原生端点 ================================

### 健康检查（含自定义公网连通性检测）
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### 应用信息（含时区信息）
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/info

### 查看所有可用指标名称
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics

### 查看 demo.counter 指标详情
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/demo.counter

### 查看 demo.timer 指标详情
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/demo.timer

### 查看 demo.queue.size 指标详情
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/demo.queue.size

### 查看 demo.request.size 指标详情
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/demo.request.size
